</aside>
<p>Hi, on the build settings everything seems to be ok. And the 404 error is returned by Vercel because they don’t recognize that subdomain. Is the domain in vercel correctly set up?<br>
<a href="https://vercel.com/your-username/your-project-name/settings/domains" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">https://vercel.com/your-username/your-project-name/settings/domains</a></p>
<p>Is a screen like this one:<br>
</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/c/c85872534de35e4455cbf7b5af0f4b64d41844e3.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/c85872534de35e4455cbf7b5af0f4b64d41844e3" title="image"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/c85872534de35e4455cbf7b5af0f4b64d41844e3_2_690x313.png" alt="image" data-base62-sha1="sAkZnDN0fd9X5dMpx01AW8BnwST" width="690" height="313" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/c85872534de35e4455cbf7b5af0f4b64d41844e3_2_690x313.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/c85872534de35e4455cbf7b5af0f4b64d41844e3_2_1035x469.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/c85872534de35e4455cbf7b5af0f4b64d41844e3_2_1380x626.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/c85872534de35e4455cbf7b5af0f4b64d41844e3_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>Also, another thing to check is the url returned by the terminal once you do npx vercel:<br>
(The Preview One). Is it the same as this one “<a href="https://mikitours-frontity.vercel.app/" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">https://mikitours-frontity.vercel.app/</a>”<br>
</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/2/25b4c2b0e12bff3fcec9865d0daa7254b66476dd.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/25b4c2b0e12bff3fcec9865d0daa7254b66476dd" title="image"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/25b4c2b0e12bff3fcec9865d0daa7254b66476dd_2_690x239.png" alt="image" data-base62-sha1="5nyWwNwu9PXqKPGQUMiBSZJiFn7" width="690" height="239" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/25b4c2b0e12bff3fcec9865d0daa7254b66476dd_2_690x239.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/2/25b4c2b0e12bff3fcec9865d0daa7254b66476dd.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/2/25b4c2b0e12bff3fcec9865d0daa7254b66476dd.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/25b4c2b0e12bff3fcec9865d0daa7254b66476dd_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
