      <item>
        <title>Deployment issue with Vercel</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Hussein]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hi I think the error is because you are visting <a href="https://mikitours-frontity.vercel.app/" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">https://mikitours-frontity.vercel.app/</a> which is the production url for vercel.</p>
<p><strong>npx vercel</strong> serve the website in development<br>
To launch the build to production you have to execute <strong>npx vercel --prod</strong> after executing <strong>npx vercel</strong></p>
<p>Anyways, the development url will be something like this <strong>vercelProjectName-vercelUsername.vercel.app</strong> instead of <strong>vercelProjectName.vercel.app</strong> which is the production build<br>
</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/2/25b4c2b0e12bff3fcec9865d0daa7254b66476dd.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/25b4c2b0e12bff3fcec9865d0daa7254b66476dd" title="image"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/25b4c2b0e12bff3fcec9865d0daa7254b66476dd_2_690x239.png" alt="image" data-base62-sha1="5nyWwNwu9PXqKPGQUMiBSZJiFn7" width="690" height="239" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/25b4c2b0e12bff3fcec9865d0daa7254b66476dd_2_690x239.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/2/25b4c2b0e12bff3fcec9865d0daa7254b66476dd.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/2/25b4c2b0e12bff3fcec9865d0daa7254b66476dd.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/25b4c2b0e12bff3fcec9865d0daa7254b66476dd_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
          <p><a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/deployment-issue-with-vercel/4237/3">Read full topic</a></p>
